o---------------o
| SPACK HISTORY |
o---------------o


Version 0.9.1 (2016-04-06)
-----------

** Bug fixes:

- Made "make_config.py" compatible with Python 2.6
- Made the build compatible with older GCC 4.x versions.


Version 0.9 (2015-04-20)
-----------

** Improvements:

- Added a configuration file for spack Fortran generator containing:
     + the mechanism name,
     + an optional function suffix,
     + if aerosol formation is enabled.
- Added automatic generation of the species and the molecular weights
  configuration files.
- Refactoring of the generation scripts, for added robustness and better code
  maintainability.
